
###SolutionRoot



/SolutionRoot
│
├── BL/                        # Business Logic Layer
│   ├── Api/                   # Interfaces for BL
│   ├── Models/                # Business models (DTOs, ViewModels)
│   ├── Services/              # Business logic services
│   └── BLManager.cs           # Main BL manager
│
├── Dal/                       # Data Access Layer
│   ├── Api/                   # Interfaces for DAL
│   ├── Models/                # Data models (Entities)
│   └── Services/              # Data access services
│
├── Server/                    # Web API Layer
│   ├── Controllers/           # API controllers
│   ├── MiddlewareExceptions/  # Custom middleware (e.g., error handling)
│   ├── appsettings.json       # Configuration file
│   ├── Program.cs             # Main entry point
│   └── Startup.cs             # Startup configuration
│
├── .gitignore
├── README.md
└── <SolutionName>.sln
